Program: Omnibus
Title: Between the High Velder and High Tech
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0376mbv
Last Broadcast Date: 03 January 2002
In post-apartheid South Africa, a look at modern afrikaans culture, it's historical roots and its place in South Africa today. Contributors include poet Antjie Krog and Carl Niehaus, ambassador and former ANC spokesman.